  <!-- Растение: Crimson Bulb (BudFlesh_CrimsonBulb) -->
  <ThingDef ParentName="PlantBaseNonEdible">
    <defName>BudFlesh_CrimsonBulb</defName>
    <label>Crimson Bulb</label>
    <description>A fleshy bulb that anchors itself deep into the soil, its veins spreading outward like roots seeking lifeblood. From this grotesque core rises a blade, slowly shaped by the plant’s pulsating growth. The more life surrounds it, the faster it matures, until the weapon is ready to be severed from its host and wielded in battle.</description>
