  <!-- Растение: Ferrite Fangroot (BudFlesh_FerriteFangroot) -->
  <ThingDef ParentName="PlantBaseNonEdible">
    <defName>BudFlesh_FerriteFangroot</defName>
    <label>Ferrite Fangroot</label>
    <description>A grotesque plant born from the fusion of living flesh and ferrite metal. Its roots writhe like tendrils, drawing strength from the soil and feeding a pulsating core with a single watchful eye. From this eye sprouts a jagged ferrite blade, grown as part of the organism itself. Once fully matured, the plant can be harvested, yielding a unique living weapon. Only those strong enough to withstand its gaze and hunger may claim the blade.</description>
